<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kuklinc Server</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{
font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
background:#0b140b;
color:white;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0b140b,#0f2f0f);
}

h1{
font-size:64px;
font-weight:800;
color:#39ff88;
text-shadow:0 0 25px #39ff88;
}

.subtitle{
margin-top:20px;
font-weight:300;
opacity:0.8;
font-size:20px;
}

.ip{
margin-top:35px;
padding:18px 40px;
border:2px solid #39ff88;
border-radius:14px;
font-weight:600;
font-size:18px;
background:rgba(57,255,136,0.08);
transition:0.3s;
}

.ip:hover{
box-shadow:0 0 25px #39ff88;
transform:scale(1.05);
}

.section{
padding:80px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.cards{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:30px;
margin-top:40px;
}

.card{
background:#111c11;
padding:30px;
border-radius:16px;
width:280px;
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(57,255,136,0.3);
}

.card h3{
color:#39ff88;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

footer{
padding:25px;
text-align:center;
background:#050805;
font-size:14px;
opacity:0.6;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
<h1>KUKLINC</h1>
<div class="subtitle">Moderný Minecraft Survival Server</div>
<div class="ip">mc.kuklincserver.online</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>Čo ťa čaká?</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card">
<h3>Survival</h3>
<p>Vyvážená ekonomika a ochrana proti griefu.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Eventy</h3>
<p>Pravidelné turnaje a špeciálne odmeny.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Komunita</h3>
<p>Aktívni hráči a stabilný server.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Kuklinc Server
</footer>

</body>
</html>
